About this page

Hoomeamea is a repository of grand challenge case studies in modeling and simulation. It is powered by MediaWiki, the same wiki technology that runs the Wikipedia project. The word "Hoomeamea" comes from native Hawaiian (like "wiki") and translates to "simulation".
